comment: Burks (UTA) initiates the contact when he extends his leg into Ibaka (OKC) on the jump shot. The contact by Burks is not enough for an offensive foul.
Favors (UTA) is in the lane without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Burks (UTA) and Durant (OKC) make incidental contact with one another while establishing position on the perimeter.
Booker (UTA) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact from Durant (OKC) on the play to basket.
Booker (UTA) extends his arm into Westbrook's (OKC) body and affects his movement to the basket.
LATR shows Adams (OKC) make contact with Favors' (UTA) body and affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) clears the lane prior to 3 seconds elapsing.
Waiters (OKC) makes contact with Hood (UTA) that affects his RSBQ on the perimeter.
Burks (UTA) releases his dribble prior to moving his pivot foot.
Westbrook (OKC) maintains legal guarding position on the jump shot by Burks (UTA).
Ibaka (OKC) sets the screen on Hayward (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ibaka (OKC) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Hayward (UTA).
Ibaka (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Burks' (UTA) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Ibaka (OKC) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Favors' (UTA) shot attempt.
Ingles (UTA) commits a take foul on Westbrook (OKC).
